### Transaction Filtering Examples
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### Variables
@accountId = ACC-12345
@fromDate = 2024-01-01T00:00:00Z
@toDate = 2024-01-31T23:59:59Z

###############################################
# Setup: Create Test Transactions
###############################################

### Create Transfer Transaction 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-001",
  "toAccount": "ACC-002",
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### Create Transfer Transaction 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-001",
  "toAccount": "ACC-003",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "TRANSFER"
}

### Create Deposit Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
